{"tid":774173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華：貿易戰如1號戒備信號　","createTime":"2018-08-10T06:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T08:18:08.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"450d052b3a37d672fedf6c540df70a9572458bac","tid":774173,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:25:35.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華接受本台訪問時表示，美國先後提出向價值500億美元，及2000億美元內地入口貨品徵收25%關稅，影響經香港轉口到美國的內地產品總值1365億港元，佔香港整體貨物出口總值3.5%，亦佔內地經香港轉口至美國的產品總值49%。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，內地提出反制關稅措施，包括向價值500億美元徵收25%關稅，及向價值600億美元美國入口貨品徵收介乎5-25%關稅，影響經香港轉口到內地的美國產品總值512億港元，佔香港整體貨物出口總值1.3%，亦佔美國經香港轉口至內地的產品總值70%。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華形容中美貿易戰發展至現階段，相當於本港懸掛1號戒備信號，如果中美關稅措施全面落實，將佔中美經本港轉口貿易逾一半。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，貿易戰會持續進行，並非短期事件，或會拖累本港下半年出口表現轉差，至於對本港今年經濟增長影響仍有待觀察，下半年前景趨向審慎。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411669-20180810.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411669-20180810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFULIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=37447f43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411669-20180810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5d1a5c89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411669-20180810.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b017550d941913306fc79c6af2dad635d566bb2b","tid":774173,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華接受本台訪問時表示，近期與本港主要商會討論，雖然暫時不多企業直接即時受到貿易戰的影響，但企業態度已轉向審慎和開始感到憂慮。他舉例指，貿易企業要考慮在市況不明朗下應否接訂單，以及接訂單後所承受的風險；企業亦對於信貸和銀根方面有所擔心。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華指，政府會繼續與商會討論包括出口保險和信貸保證方面措施，會否有再優化的空間，以應付貿易戰可能延續的情況，他建議企業要做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，政府在年初出台針對市場拓展、產品升級轉型，及對中小企信貸支援的工作，正好在目前市況下適用。"},{"pid":"07aef35523a00923de880a81d951a329a0e2a6e0","tid":774173,"uid":58552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"姐係無事啦"},{"pid":"55607537e67101ded2dcc5eea12bcad91b848fab","tid":774173,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:38:59.000Z","msg":"實情係有如天鴿吹襲澳門<br />\n乜鳩都死哂<br />\n解放軍幫手搬兩下嘢就暈"},{"pid":"8dfede6cefc6bd0a389f3bed1053ca1cf73ea640","tid":774173,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"貿易戰如八號十號咁就死"},{"pid":"985e1f39bd9951ff142447e929614569c3519b44","tid":774173,"uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"即係冇乜影響，<br />\n咁美國整個十號波畀支那嘆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d796de3b68908081cf9b3fea5f4fb9518d588d","tid":774173,"uid":144035,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39e48aaf7770b613d1e2330763e7d637ed16e883","tid":774173,"uid":104699,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:55:17.000Z","msg":"屌你死港獨，要堅定支持一個中國政策，唔收香港關稅即係分裂國家"},{"pid":"fd975a7a3b41dc632dae8ce255ff40c516af6804","tid":774173,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"即係準時返工就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348ba88569d1643a66ca6b93e959b7d09b594435","tid":774173,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd975a7a3b41dc632dae8ce255ff40c516af6804","tid":774173,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"即係準時返工就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93ad03a92d026a23d78f835654a4676873131c2","tid":774173,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"大陸打到8號喇"},{"pid":"02353ad2655e08693f2bd860ff02b7116232ac6a","tid":774173,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917dbe6c4a0afe2ff6846c1aa0a59ab3ed937292","tid":774173,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"1號風球市民如常出街 如常工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e72c832edd859355487662dde2863bb62c319cb","tid":774173,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:16:58.000Z","msg":"走啦7頭"},{"pid":"5e4b1b4ef4569877fa886b87a49826cdf27fdfac","tid":774173,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"家下港商都轉晒支那牌, 數字本身已經唔準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}